Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:21.90,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(130,130)}守電話·宣佈緊急事態
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.68,0:24:14.83,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 颱風過後·虛像與實像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尿出來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:31.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「司…令部直…通高…度緊…急非…常事\N…態用指…令傳…達線…路維…護確…認任…務」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名堂真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是非常重要的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:40.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是失敗了 可能小隊全員都會受到懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:48.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據情況 有可能發起第一警戒態勢\N給這區域的所有分隊下達緊急出動準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:53.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊 責任非常重大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:57.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼樣的任務呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:58.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:02.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守電話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:11.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這電話是連接首都的熱線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:13.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它有響過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 謝天謝地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:24.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 雖然響了就麻煩\N但如果在真正需要的時候不響的話 會更麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:28.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以半年一度 確認線路是否連通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:29.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司…司…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 好好記住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「司令部直通非常緊急…」 誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:42.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是「司令部直通高度非常事…」 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:49.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「司令部直通高度緊急非常事態用指令傳達線路維護確認任務」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:50.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:55.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做我做我要做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:58.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我做那個任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:01.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很想通一通電話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要這麼興奮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:07.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本構造是跟建御雷神的內部通話一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是距離離得遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:14.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然可以跟距離很遠的人說話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:21.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 的確跟完全見不到面的人說話 感覺不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:24.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 弄熟了就覺得沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:28.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有個麻煩 不知道今天什麼時候打過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:30.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣你也願意做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:31.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:36.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那你今天整天守著電話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:42.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呤呤呤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:49.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是赫爾維西亞陸軍第1121號要塞 空深彼方二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:56.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 聽完電話了就把它放回原位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:57.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲…菲莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:44.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西婭姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得都覺得悶熱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火車來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火車？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:55.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必須盡快送到司令部的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:58.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯下個星期來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要去車站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你好好守電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:04.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一有什麼差錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:10.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟糕的情況 有可能會被認為這裡受到攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好守住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:36.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:37.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有見到乃繪留了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:47.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在機庫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:51.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 中午想吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣 今天是我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:00.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:07.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你和暮羽為什麼一到我值日做飯的時候 什麼都不讓我做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:11.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來之前 我也做得不少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道也應該不差的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:19.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確味道沒有外觀那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:21.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:24.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 味道鮮明 很美的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:30.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 那今天就比平時更賣力地做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:34.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩 是直美姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:41.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:45.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我要守著電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:50.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:53.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:01.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混砧板渣的三文治 我可不想再吃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:06.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們喝吧 是蘋果汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是給我們批發蘋果汁的農家自製的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:17.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這些跟我們的卡巴度斯是親戚咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 已經露餡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當禮物的兩瓶就夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:35.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有城鎮的工商會的集會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:43.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們受他們各方面的通融 按照慣例也得給他們點禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:44.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:45.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:50.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 她們一直都拚命瞞著的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會露餡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:56.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:57.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:01.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機會再給你說明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:06.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 直美姐也一起吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:10.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 要我也去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 登在這星期報紙上的新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎大家都想聽聽軍方的正式說明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:18.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:22.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說休戰協定的會議進展不順的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:28.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把賠款額和領土劃分什麼的一一決定好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖延是正常的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:37.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過嘛 工會那些大叔的目的其實也就是想見見你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:41.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說你在潑水節上當炎之少女後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉絲就多了起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩死了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:52.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 貌似我不得不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身心也早已經是要塞少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人也能完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:00.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:01.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 給你這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的舊書 有點過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是小號的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了太美了太美了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的喇叭也變得像樣起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:26.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是獎勵你認真練習的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:30.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有了這書 你也不會犯瞌睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 這就是C
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:44.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D E F G
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:47.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天也要結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乃 在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:35.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了 晾的衣服要濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡院屬於作戰活動範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:52.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 來玩吧{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub註釋: 下一行不需要檢查時間軸 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:58.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 來玩吧{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:12:00.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:12.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:16.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 晾的衣服沒濕真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:17.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:22.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 突然要您幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:27.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意 我們才是 突然造訪真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:32.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就得回到托雷茲 我是來道別的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不用給當兵的道別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這樣說話啊 誠也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:45.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子好像也對你們各位做過不禮貌的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:49.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天也是想來道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:51.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他幾位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:57.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫梨旺小姐嗎 那位黑髮的小姐也不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:57.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:01.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 可以的話真想見上一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:05.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本書是你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:06.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:10.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小號的書 是梨旺前輩給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:13.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:18.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒沒 失禮了 我自言自語
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:21.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方一個人看家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:32.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部直通高度緊急非常事態用指令傳達線路維護確認任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:33.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…執行中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:40.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 是在等這個響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:41.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:46.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我是第一次用 有點緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:50.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己能不能好好說話呢…什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要練習一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:14:00.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 由美奈也去參加工會集會了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:06.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她去取工會各位的捐贈物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:07.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 請喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:15.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 誠也也快喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:19.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然喝 不過別以為這就拉攏到我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:31.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美汐你們看得出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的就是電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:50.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們喜歡 我偶爾會做給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 誠也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:02.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:04.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 好厲害啊 誠也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得很清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 一開始要說「喂」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:10.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是打電話的規定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:15.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:20.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 真的 真的能聽到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個練習就好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:23.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:27.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:36.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是赫爾維西亞陸軍第1121號要塞 空深彼方二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:38.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:41.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩您專程打來電話 在下感到慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:43.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:47.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 小鳥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美汐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:50.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:51.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:10.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:33.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 祭司爺爺和我們那裡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:55.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸神們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:06.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等失態 不是來表示一直以來的感謝和歉意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然玩獵奇起來 還給人家添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:12.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們今晚沒飯吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:13.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:15.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒得吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:23.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒問題了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你衣服也濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 還有換的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有妙計
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:43.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這衣服…羞死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼的華麗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 謝謝你 由美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這衣服我會洗好再還你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:56.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 送給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對孩子們來說太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:04.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不會有其他人比彼方更適合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次還能陪我們玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠也下次也要來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:15.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時間我再來陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:30.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們告辭了 願您們萬福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感…感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:41.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 要收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛忘了 上廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:21.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尿出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人…快點來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那群大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:26.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 彼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前…輩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:32.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 請救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…怎麼了 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:37.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:41.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快尿出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:44.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去 會憋出病的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:46.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直憋著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:52.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道說她耿直還是敦實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:04.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:10.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 我已經一步也動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:14.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個沒時運的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:22.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是赫爾維西亞陸軍第1121小隊 梨旺·和宮軍士長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:29.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 聽說要跟你們那邊確認線路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:30.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就請求…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:32.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我沒有逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:39.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 你只是沒有原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:43.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你還找我什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:47.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 拯救這個國家 拯救赫爾維西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:57.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乃 難道你一直…從早上開始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:00.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在廁所很好睡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:02.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:07.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:10.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼穿得這麼可愛啊 小彼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:14.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你們兩個在走廊幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:16.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方摔倒了 站不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:18.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:21.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快站起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:27.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你沒辦法啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:29.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬌氣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:30.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…八要…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:34.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:36.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八要啊！
